1
00:01:24,600 --> 00:01:25,720
Ji Bai, run!

2
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:28,960
Impossible.

3
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:30,520
It must be that the poisonous bug

4
00:01:30,520 --> 00:01:32,840
was soaked in the mother bug's blood for too short a time,

5
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:35,240
so it didn't take full effect on him.

6
00:01:57,080 --> 00:01:57,960
This poisonous bug of yours

7
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:59,280
is completely useless.

8
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:00,480
What use are you to me?

9
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:01,760
What a waste

10
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,620
of all the support I've given you.

11
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:04,880
My Lord,

12
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:05,880
rest assured.

13
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:07,240
I will definitely capture them both

14
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:08,500
to appease your anger.

15
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:10,370
I certainly won't let you down.

16
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:13,400
You'd better keep your word.

17
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,060
Otherwise,

18
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,640
I'll stuff all those bugs

19
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,240
right into your mouth.

20
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:18,920
I understand.

21
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,640
I will not fail you.

22
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:25,240
Xiao Heyan,

23
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:26,840
you can't escape.

24
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:29,079
I will never let you get away.

25
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,460
Yan Quezuo.

26
00:02:48,720 --> 00:02:49,640
Just you wait.

27
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,160
When the time comes,

28
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,200
I will make you suffer

29
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:53,680
a fate worse than death.

30
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:54,920
I'll make you regret

31
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:56,650
everything you did to me today.

32
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:06,580
It seems

33
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:08,320
this is the medical hall.

34
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:09,890
Strange.

35
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:12,680
Why isn't Dr. Ji at the clinic today?

36
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:14,770
The old owner just passed away,

37
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,640
and the new owner is nowhere to be found.

38
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:18,440
Could something have happened?

39
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:20,600
It's also possible

40
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:22,680
she got tied up by patients at that house.

41
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,200
I was just about to go check.

42
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:24,640
Okay.

43
00:03:24,760 --> 00:03:25,760
I'll go with you.

44
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:26,570
How about

45
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:27,900
we all go together?

46
00:03:29,760 --> 00:03:32,020
I'm looking for Dr. Ji for treatment too.

47
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:33,920
After you.

48
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:34,450
Let's go.

49
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:36,720
This house you mentioned,

50
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:38,530
what kind of place is it?

51
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,720
It's a run-down house at the end of the street.

52
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:41,960
Dr. Ji lives there.

53
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:42,560
Usually,

54
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:44,600
she sees patients there often too.

55
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:45,000
Right.

56
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,120
Dr. Ji,

57
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:49,560
besides her regular consultations at the Du Family Clinic,

58
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,800
she goes there every day

59
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:52,280
to treat the poor for free.

60
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:55,120
It seems my apprentice

61
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:56,579
has really improved a lot.

62
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:57,120
Huh?

63
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,210
What did you say?

64
00:03:59,240 --> 00:03:59,760
I said,

65
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:01,720
Dr. Ji is truly kind and skilled.

66
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:02,960
A living Hua Tuo.

67
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,200
Exactly.

68
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:06,520
Ever since Dr. Ji came to our Sitai Town,

69
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:08,160
she has helped countless people.

70
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,090
I hope this time,

71
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:11,200
she's really just stuck at the house

72
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:12,840
and nothing bad has happened.

73
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:13,760
What happened?

74
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:17,339
You don't know yet?

75
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:19,200
This morning,

76
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:21,180
a dead body was found in the alley.

77
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:23,880
I heard it was someone from the escort agency.

78
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:25,120
They hadn't been dead for long.

79
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:26,450
The body was still warm.

80
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,280
I just got back from out of town,

81
00:04:29,280 --> 00:04:30,210
so I didn't know.

82
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,380
The town

83
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:33,800
might be caught up in some vendetta.

84
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:35,440
Everyone is very uneasy.

85
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:36,480
Yeah.

86
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:38,880
Heaven bless Dr. Ji,

87
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:40,760
I hope she doesn't get involved.

88
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:45,000
Heaven protects the worthy.

89
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,060
Dr. Ji will be fine.

90
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,200
Let's go.

91
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:19,730
This pill will stabilize your condition for now.

92
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:26,280
Ji Bai.

93
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:29,320
I'm the one they want.

94
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,360
You go.

95
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,440
Leave me.

96
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:35,200
I won't give up on you.

97
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:36,720
Hang in there.

98
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,520
You made me many promises.

99
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:40,159
If you hold on,

100
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,200
I'll agree to everything

101
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,720
you said before. Okay?

102
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:45,240
Ji Bai.

103
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:47,640
Don't be silly.

104
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,080
We are...

105
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:49,800
No.

106
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,400
Just no.

107
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,040
You have to hold on.

108
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:56,659
I won't let you give up.

109
00:05:56,960 --> 00:05:57,760
You won't.

110
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:59,080
And neither will I.

111
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:00,680
If you hold on,

112
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:02,360
I'll say yes to everything

113
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:04,240
you've ever said.

114
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,400
Okay?

115
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,000
Xiao Heyan.

116
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:14,200
We have so many unfulfilled dreams and promises.

117
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:15,880
From childhood,

118
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:17,760
and now.

119
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:20,400
Is that right?

120
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:21,880
You said

121
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:24,520
we'd travel the world together.

122
00:06:24,840 --> 00:06:25,960
I'd practice medicine

123
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:26,960
to help the world,

124
00:06:27,640 --> 00:06:28,840
and you'd protect me.

125
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,080
You remember.

126
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:37,370
You remember it so clearly.

127
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,840
Little Master Ji.

128
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:51,040
So you have fallen for me.

129
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:00,000
I like you.

130
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:14,960
Sir.

131
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,160
Sir.

132
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:21,160
There should be a first aid kit in the room.

133
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:23,160
Could you two please help me find it?

134
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:37,680
You take over.

135
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:38,930
I'll look for it.

136
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,800
Interlock your fingers.

137
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:44,640
Stack the heels of your hands.

138
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:46,120
Keep your palms slightly raised.

139
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,520
Keep your arms straight.

140
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:49,440
Lean forward.

141
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,200
Pivot from your hips.

142
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,120
Use your upper body weight.

143
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,440
Press straight down.

144
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:56,760
Compress about two inches deep.

145
00:07:58,800 --> 00:07:59,600
Let me do it.

146
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:11,960
Miss,

147
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:13,930
your technique is incredible.

148
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:16,700
We've never seen anyone save a person like this.

149
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:18,980
You flatter me.

150
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:20,820
Could I trouble you two

151
00:08:20,840 --> 00:08:22,370
to help me carry him inside?

152
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:40,640
We can't give up yet.

153
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,900
They're bound to catch up.

154
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:44,640
Right now, we...

155
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:51,080
You're reaching your limit.

156
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:52,920
Let's take a break.

157
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,760
I finally found you.

158
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:00,720
Chuyun.

159
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:01,960
Why are you here?

160
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,480
Did Duyu send you?

161
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,160
No.

162
00:09:04,560 --> 00:09:06,040
I'm not here for Duyu.

163
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:08,680
I have something important to tell you.

164
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:10,440
What is it?

165
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,240
Make it quick.

166
00:09:11,400 --> 00:09:12,930
We don't have time to waste.

167
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:15,480
About

168
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:17,440
the clue you're looking for,

169
00:09:18,520 --> 00:09:19,560
I know something.

170
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:21,600
What do you know?

171
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,760
It's not safe here.

172
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:28,200
They're still looking for you.

173
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:30,240
Let's find a safe place to talk.

174
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:31,240
Okay.

175
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:32,490
Lead the way.

176
00:09:32,920 --> 00:09:33,520
Ji Bai.

177
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,050
Don't worry.

178
00:09:36,920 --> 00:09:38,240
Given the situation,

179
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:40,360
we have to trust her for now.

180
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,720
If anything happens,

181
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:44,520
I'll protect you.

182
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,570
I should be the one saying that.

183
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:51,880
Um, I'm still here.

184
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:54,280
Then please lead the way.

185
00:10:08,680 --> 00:10:10,320
He's out of danger now.

186
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,810
He just needs some rest.

187
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:15,720
Little Jibai must be in some kind of danger.

188
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:19,240
Otherwise, she wouldn't leave so many patients unattended.

189
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:21,240
Please take care of that gentleman.

190
00:10:34,800 --> 00:10:35,840
We've arrived.

191
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,000
It's well hidden.

192
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,560
No one can find this place.

193
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:39,480
Chuyun,

194
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:40,720
thank you.

195
00:10:58,920 --> 00:10:59,720
Actually,

196
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,820
I'm the one who should apologize.

197
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:05,660
You're the ones who saved my life,

198
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,480
yet I betrayed you.

199
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:09,880
Betrayed?

200
00:11:10,880 --> 00:11:11,960
What do you mean?

201
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:16,000
I've been working for Du Yu.

202
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,720
I helped him monitor you

203
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:20,260
and track your movements.

204
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:24,920
Then why tell us this now?

205
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:27,780
Because...

206
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:30,280
After I regained my sight,

207
00:11:30,760 --> 00:11:32,880
I found out Du Yu killed my family

208
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,600
and pretended to save me.

209
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:37,010
He's been lying to me all along.

210
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:38,680
I was deceived by him

211
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:40,800
and fell in love with him.

212
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:42,720
I truly regret it.

213
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:45,280
So I want to help you.

214
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:47,440
I want to tell you everything I know.

215
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:22,560
Wu, Zhang, Li, Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng.

216
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:21,840
Yi, Yi, Nan.

217
00:12:22,560 --> 00:12:24,690
Wu, Zhang, Li, Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng.

218
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:51,280
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

219
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:52,360
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

220
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:56,920
Lyu, Sun, Zhang, Meng

221
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:56,920
Pan, Xiu, Long.

222
00:12:56,920 --> 00:12:57,000
Lyu, Sun.

223
00:12:56,920 --> 00:12:57,000
Pan.

224
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:57,960
Lyu, Sun, Zhang, Meng.
